  "body": "On electron remixd spawn doesn't have the right path environment to execute commands like npx.  Basically process.env doesn't have the default paths when electron is executed as a standalone GUI. This is due to the shell it inherits from. It can be fixed in several ways. Another option can also be to let the user provide a .env file in the workspace if the path can't be found. ",
